{
  "id": "622b0c7c8974a6001dda7b55",
  "title": "問いをタイトルにしがち",
  "created": 1646988413,
  "updated": 1646988413,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "622b0c7c8974a6001dda7b55",
      "text": "問いをタイトルにしがち",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1646988413,
      "updated": 1646988413
    },
    {
      "id": "622b0c7caff09e00004e6ed9",
      "text": "from [思考の結節点2022-03-11]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1646988413,
      "updated": 1646988413
    },
    {
      "id": "622b0c7caff09e00004e6eda",
      "text": "問いをタイトルにしがち",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1646988413,
      "updated": 1646988413
    },
    {
      "id": "622b0c7caff09e00004e6edb",
      "text": "　問いが箇条書きの根になり、その下に考察が展開された場合、根が一番上にあるせいでタイトルにしてしまう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1646988413,
      "updated": 1646988413
    },
    {
      "id": "622b0c7caff09e00004e6edc",
      "text": "　　結論が出たなら結論をタイトルにした方がいい？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1646988413,
      "updated": 1646988413
    },
    {
      "id": "622b0c7caff09e00004e6edd",
      "text": "　　将来、同じ問いについて違う結論が出る可能性もある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1646988413,
      "updated": 1646988413
    },
    {
      "id": "622b0c7caff09e00004e6ede",
      "text": "　　　問い部分をリンクにする？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1646988413,
      "updated": 1646988413
    },
    {
      "id": "622b0c7caff09e00004e6edf",
      "text": "　具体例",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1646988413,
      "updated": 1646988413
    },
    {
      "id": "622b0c7caff09e00004e6ee0",
      "text": "　　before「なぜ老害を研究するのか」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1646988413,
      "updated": 1646988413
    },
    {
      "id": "622b0c7caff09e00004e6ee1",
      "text": "　　after「老害化しない技術が人生全体での知的生産性向上に有益」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1646988413,
      "updated": 1646988413
    },
    {
      "id": "622b0c7caff09e00004e6ee2",
      "text": "関連",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1646988413,
      "updated": 1646988413
    },
    {
      "id": "622b0c7caff09e00004e6ee3",
      "text": "\t　[ドアは部屋自体ではない]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1646988413,
      "updated": 1646988413
    },
